5 A BILL
6 TO BE ENTITLED
7 AN ACT
8
9 Relating to public education employees; to amend
10 Section 16-22-9, Code of Alabama 1975; to revise the
11 definition of "education authority" for purposes of sick
12 leave; to require the State Board of Education to adopt a
13 model policy relating to sick leave; to require the model
14 policy to authorize the direct donation of sick leave between
15 education employees employed by any educational authority; to
16 require educational authorities to implement the model policy;
17 to require policies developed by the sick leave bank committee
18 to be approved by the educational authority; to further
19 provide for the duties of sick leave bank committees; and to
20 further provide for sick leave banks and catastrophic sick
21 leave.
22 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
